<body>

<div class="container-narrow">

    <div class="masthead">
        <ul class="nav nav-pills pull-right">
            <li><a href="courses.html">Courses</a></li>
            <li><a href="about.html">About</a></li>
            <li><a href="contact.html">Contact</a></li>
            <% if (!req.isAuthenticated()) { %>
                <li><a href="#login" data-toggle="modal">Login</a></li>
                <li><a href="#signup" data-toggle="modal">Sign Up</a></li>

            <% } else { %>
                <li><a href="#profile" ><%=req.user.name%></a></li>
            <% } %>

        </ul>
        <h3 class="muted"><a href="index.html">KinoEdu</a></h3>
    </div>

    <hr></hr>

    <div class="jumbotron">
        <h1>NextGen Learning Platform!</h1>
        <p class="lead">Learning is now an integral part any company. Over last few years, learning has transformed from leaps and bounds. Video Tutorial, Month long Courses, Homework , Quiz and showcase progress and certification on Social Networks are now the key essense. Forming communities around learning a set of skills is the key thing today</p>
        <a class="btn btn-large btn-success" href="#signup" data-toggle="modal">Sign up today</a>
    </div>

    <hr></hr>
    <div class="flex-video">
        <iframe class="youtube-player" type="text/html" width="640" height="385" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/kdUMlBf1aA4" allowfullscreen frameborder="0">
        </iframe>
    </div>

    <hr></hr>

    <div class="row-fluid marketing">
        <div class="span6">
            <h4>Video Instructions</h4>
            <p>Ability to embed Youtube, Vimeo video tutorial in your courses.</p>

            <h4>Short Quiz</h4>
            <p>Immediate Short Quiz enables person to validate candidate's understanding,before stepping to next lesson.</p>

            <h4>Home Work</h4>
            <p>Series of Homework complete over days/week helps candidate really polish their skills.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="span6">
            <h4>Certification Center</h4>
            <p>The Certification Center helps a candidate store and showcase their certifications.</p>

            <h4>Social Media</h4>
            <p>Ability to push Certifications or Progress on a certain course to Facebook, Google+, Twitter and Linkedin.</p>

            <h4>Social Community</h4>
            <p>Build Social Communities around skills. Request experts in the community to put up newer courses and certifications.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <hr></hr>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>&copy; KinoEdu 2013</p>
    </div>

</div> <!-- /container -->


<!-- Modal -->
<div id="signup" class="modal hide fade" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="myModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
    <section data-aura-widget="signup"></section>
</div>


<!-- Modal -->
<div id="login" class="modal hide fade" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="myModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
